# The way into my parlor #

507
00:51:41,864 --> 00:51:45,353
# Is up a winding stair #

508
00:51:45,353 --> 00:51:50,792
# And I have many
curious little things #

509
00:51:50,792 --> 00:51:54,952
# To show you when you're there #

510
00:51:54,952 --> 00:51:57,959
# Oh no no said the fly #

511
00:51:57,959 --> 00:52:00,775
# To ask me is in vain #

